captions.text: Hey there, babe!
Batman!  How did you get in here?
The window of course.
Sorry about the lock.  I had to break it.
Why can't you just knock like a normal human being?

Babe, you know the answer to that.  It's
because I'm Batman.

Well you're going to have to go be Batman
somewhere else.
Emmet's going to be here any minute...
and we're going to dinner.
Ah!  Date night.
I miss those.
You never showed up to those!
So how are things going now that you have an "average" boyfriend for a change?
Hey!
I mean it's gotta be a big step down from the Bat Man.
He doesn't even have a secret identity.
He has charm.
I have charisma!
He's caring.
I have abs!
He has a heart!
I have a bat mobile!
What are you trying to say?
I'm just saying a girl like you with a guy like him...
You sure you're okay settling with someone so...
un hot?
*door bell*
whoooooaaaaaaah
Hey babe!  Sorry I'm late.  I just got through stopping a genocide through a dance-off!
I'll have to tell you about it!
You look... different.
Oh yeah! I've been at the gym lately.
I've come a long way from the days when I hung out at the park for recreation.
So Batman, What were you saying about, Emmet?

Shh! Sweetheart we need to keep that on
the down low remember it's Star Lord.
Oh right!  I forgot! (whispers) It's your secret identity!
Care to take a whirl in my new ride?
I just got it all fixed up.
I'd love to!
He still doesn't have a Batmobile!
Wooohoooooo!
Whoa.
Okay, that's kind of cool.
I can't stop!
